headline: TD Cowen Raises Digital Realty Trust (DLR) Target on Strong Q4 Performance
summary: Digital Realty Trust, Inc. (NYSE:DLR) is included among the 14 Best Real Estate Stocks to Buy According to Hedge Funds. On February 6, TD Cowen raised its price recommendation on Digital Realty Trust, Inc. (NYSE:DLR) to $185 from $179. The analyst kept a Hold rating on the shares. The firm pointed to stronger-than-expected fourth-quarter results […]
